name: Milk Bath
description:
Join our Discord to see more images and upcoming updates!

Introduction

Milk Bath is a LoRA which was trained on mostly nude woman lying in milk water. Cleopatra also added honey so the trigger word contains honey too.

Training Resolution: 512x768 (2:3) + 768x512 (3:2)

Trained on Real Hot Mix but also works on other models.

How to Use

Strenght 0.4-0.8

Lower the value if you want to reduce nudes or if you want to show other objects.

CFG 5-7

Prompts

woman lying in milkandhoney (for nudes)

(something lying in milkandhoney:1.2) to show something (add woman to negative)

If you just want milkandhoney without the bath tub, add bath tub to negative (works not in all cases).

front view, rear view, side view if you depict a woman

Some objects just float on the water and just don't work even if you add strenght. Objects that are usually in water work better. See promo images for more examples and see the LoRA metadata for a full tag list on how to control nudes.
